<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Order Confirmation: Thank You for Your Purchase!</h1>

  <p>Dear <%= @buyer.name %>,</p>

  <p>Thank you for placing an order with Adversal. We are excited to confirm your purchase. Here are the order details:</p>

  <p>
    Order Number: <%= @order.number %><br>
    Product Name: <%= @product.title %><br>
  </p>

  <p>
    Thank you for choosing Adversal.
    Please note that for specific details regarding the product, delivery, or any other inquiries, we recommend reaching out directly to the seller at <%= @product.seller.email %>
  </p>

  <p>
    If you have any general questions or concerns, our customer support is here to assist you.
  </p>

  <p>Best regards,<br>
    Adversal
  </p>
</body>
</html>